Actions.Text: AMEND (T) AND RECOMMIT TO ENVIRONMENTAL CONSERVATION

Title: Authorizes the feeding of white-tailed deer in Sullivan county
Summary: Authorizes the feeding of white-tailed deer in Sullivan county until January 1, 2026 or until the legislature determines that the population warrants that such permission be rescinded.
ActClause: AN ACT authorizing the feeding of white-tailed deer in Sullivan county
